---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---
<Layout title="About and Sustainability | One Earth Gifting" description="Our story, mission and sustainability commitments. A venture of One Earth Beyond Ltd.">

  <div class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Our story</p>
      <h1>Gifting that gives back</h1>
      <p>One Earth Gifting is the sustainable gifting venture of One Earth Beyond Ltd. A company built around the belief that business can be a force for good.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Our mission</p>
          <h2>Gifts with purpose, not just pretty packaging</h2>
          <p>We started One Earth Gifting because we were tired of corporate gifts that ended up in landfill. Cheap, plastic wrapped and forgotten. We wanted to create something different: gifts that people actually love, from makers who are paid fairly, that leave the planet better than we found it.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:1rem;">Every product in our range is handpicked against strict ethical, environmental and quality criteria. If it doesn't pass our test, it doesn't make the cut.</p>
          <a href="/shop" class="btn btn-ghost" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">Browse our collection</a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <video autoplay muted loop playsinline style="border-radius:var(--radius-lg);width:100%;background:var(--sand);min-height:280px;object-fit:cover;display:block;">
            <source src="/video/care.mp4" type="video/mp4">
          </video>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section" style="background:var(--forest);color:var(--white);" id="sustainability">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="max-width:660px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
        <p class="eyebrow" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);">Our commitment to forests</p>
        <h2 style="color:var(--white);">A Tree With Every Sale</h2>
        <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.78);font-size:1.02rem;margin-bottom:2rem;">Every order placed on One Earth Gifting directly funds the planting of one tree. We work with local non-profit organisations in some of the most heavily deforested regions of Asia, where reforestation restores both ecosystems and the communities that depend on them. This is not an offset. It is a direct act of regeneration.</p>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:3rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
          {[['1 Tree','planted per order'],['Local NGOs','our planting partners'],['100%','plastic free packaging']].map(([n,l]) => (
            <div style="text-align:center;">
              <div style="font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);">{n}</div>
              <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);">{l}</div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">What we stand for</p>
      <h2>Our sustainability commitments</h2>
      <div class="commitments">
        {[
          ['Packaging Philosophy','Every order leaves in recycled, compostable or reusable materials. We have eliminated single use plastic entirely from our supply chain.'],
          ['Supplier Ethics','We only work with suppliers who pay fair wages, respect workers\' rights, and operate transparently. Many hold GOTS, Fair Trade, or B Corp certification.'],
          ['Carbon Footprint','We measure and offset our Scope 1 and 2 emissions. Working toward full Scope 3 transparency by 2027.'],
          ['B Corp Journey','We are currently completing our B Corp Impact Assessment. We believe businesses should be accountable to people and planet. Not just profit.'],
          ['Circular Economy','Products are chosen for durability and repairability. Packaging instructions included for composting or reuse.'],
          ['Community Impact','A portion of corporate order profits supports UK food banks and environmental education programmes.'],
        ].map(([title, body]) => (
          <div class="commitment">
            <h4>{title}</h4>
            <p>{body}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section" style="background:var(--navy);color:var(--white);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);">Our parent company</p>
          <h2 style="color:var(--white);">One Earth Beyond Ltd</h2>
          <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.72);">One Earth Gifting is a venture of One Earth Beyond Ltd. A purpose-driven business consultancy helping organisations reduce their environmental impact and build for the long term.</p>
          <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.72);margin-top:1rem;">Our gifting range is an extension of that mission: proving that premium and sustainable are not in conflict.</p>
          <a href="https://oneearthbeyond.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">Visit One Earth Beyond →</a>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;">
          <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:3rem;text-align:center;">
            <div style="font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:0.5rem;">One Earth Beyond</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.84rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);">oneearthbeyond.com</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
